			<div class="question">
				<h1 style="color:#4D8DC7;">How do I use NoteMinders?</h1>
				<p>Start by creating an account. Once signed up, you'll be redirected to a create notes page. Create a note. You should receive an email confirmation with your note. Just glance at the note and give it some feedback by submitting the form at the bottom of the email/text. From then on the algorithm will send you the note via text/email right at the point at which you're most likely to forget it. Over time, (if you're honest about how much you recall) the algorithm gets smarter and will send you the note less frequently. It's completely personalized.</p>
			</div>
			
