				<h1 style="color:#4D8DC7">How do I uninstall Noteminders?</h1>
				<p>Start by signing in and going to your dashboard. That's the hub of all management tasks. You can delete your account by clicking on the account tab and clicking the delete button. If that doesn't work just click 'Contact' in the bottom field of the website on the home page. We'll get you sorted as soon as possible.</p>
